{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the crematoriums could not supply fast enough to get rid of the bodies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they were digging huge ditches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And those ditches were those with gasoline, and just put on fire, outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was an unbelievable smell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was an unbelievable knowledge, that that's happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I mean, once you are that close to it, we were so close to what's happening there that the mental and-- and-- and-- the physical was nothing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Physically, it was the best job available.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was no-- no not-- no better job, for the simple reason, although we were forbidden, [COUGHS] then, well, you are on a diet, what I told you before.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then you see food coming in from ghettos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "First of all, you know the food comes from a-- from a another Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You stuff your mouth, even if-- even if the punishment is harsh.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Punishment could have been, at that time, a shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But you stuffed your mouth and you ate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So basically, that was the best job available.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Also, that once we noticed that the jewelry is going into the smaller box, the smaller jewelry, bigger jewelry, one day the SS-- the same SS guard who was a pleasant-looking fellow, he was a German SS.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "By the way, we were-- there you had a lot of Ukrainian and Lithuanian SS, also in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this guy was pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, he basically never did anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He yelled, screamed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But he was never rough to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was brash, young, and not thinking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I grabbed like, a handful of good jewelry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But I thought it was a good jewelry and just put it in his hand.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So he looked at me first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And his reaction was it goes to the box.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
